{
  "stem": "5639.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The community was a community with a very high-developed sense-- it was a very high developed sense of volunteerism--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--of charity, and of communal responsibility.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it's not right that it was hardly-- that was a sharp division.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, I remember we had a-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who was he?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Moshke-- Moshke was, by profession, a porter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Porters were profession.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Moshke was, by profession, a porter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Moshke was very, very poor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he never came begging.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father never allowed him to come to a situation where he had to beg.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And always, before Friday, he called him to perform a task.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And for that task, he paid him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He could have well done without the task.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Made sure that the--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--perseverance of his human dignity is unscathed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was brought up in that tradition not knowing any other way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what I distinctly remember is that human dignity was sacred.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Absolutely sacred.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I was rude to our maid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was not punished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was only given to perform her task for a certain period of time, which in my mind, work is not punishment.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If I was told for two months to set the table because once I sat at the table and I said, there's no fork, or I don't like that spoon, or something like that.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was told from now on, you will be setting the table.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother's best friend was a boy who was disabled, and he studied with my brother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was never short of anything, never made to feel that because he's disabled he can't have a uniform, or he can't have another book.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
